'''Hangan'''
({{lang-my|ဟံဂံ}}; {{lang-mnw|ဟံၚ်ဂါမ်၊ကွာန်}}) is a village in [[Ye Township]] in [[Mawlamyine District]] in the [[Mon State]] of south-east [[Burma|Burma (Myanmar)]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://themimu.info/sites/themimu.info/files/documents/Myanmar_PCodes_Release-VIII.i_Sep2017_Mon.zip|title=Mon State Place Codes|work=Myanmar Information Management Unit|date=September 2017|accessdate=27 February 2018}}</ref> [[Hangan]] [[Village]] is located in the south of [[Ye]] [[Township]], about 7 miles from [[Ye]] [[Township]]About 90% of the population is [[Mon]].{{Convert|4|km|mi|<ref>[http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/ams/burma/txu-oclc-6924198-nd47-2.jpg Burma 1:250,000 topographic map, Series U542, ND 47-02 Ye] U.S. Army Map Service, December 1959</ref><br>

